cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image processing and 3D reconstruction. The use of convolutional neural networks also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The mention of geodesic coordinate maps suggests a possible connection to robotics (cs.RO) and the use of principal curvature as an indicator of planar boundaries suggests a possible connection to graphics (cs.GR).
